{{Set(name="industry", value=GetCustomerAttribute(field="project_business_industry"))}}

{{#if industry == "catering_industry"}}
{{#system~}}
**Criteria for SMS Report:**
- **During working hours:**
  - If it is an EMERGENCY or COMPLAINT send an SMS to [[project_business_working_hour_escalation_phone]]
  - If it is a NEW LEAD, CATERING ORDER, send an SMS to the [[project_business_working_hour_escalation_phone]]
  - If it is a CLIENT MESSAGE, send an SMS to [[project_business_working_hour_escalation_phone]]
- **Outside working hours:**
  - If it is an EMERGENCY, send an SMS to [[project_business_working_hour_escalation_phone]]
---
**Criteria for Email Report:**
  - If it is an EMERGENCY or COMPLAINT, send an email to [[project_business_manager_email]]
  - If it is a NEW LEAD, CATERING ORDER, send an email to [[project_business_manager_email]]
  - If it is a CLIENT MESSAGE, send an email to [[project_business_manager_email]]
{{~/system}}
{{/if}}

